article.description: — Alex Barcello scored 18 points to lead BYU past San Francisco 71-69 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Barcello scores 18 to lead BYU past San Francisco 71-69
article.linkText: Barcello scores 18 to lead BYU past San Francisco 71-69
article.story: SAN FRANCISCO -- — Alex Barcello scored 18 points to lead BYU past San Francisco 71-69 on Saturday night. Te’Jon Lucas scored 12 points for BYU (15-4, 3-1 West Coast Conference). Jamaree Bouyea led San Francisco (15-3, 2-1) with 19 points. Khalil Shabazz added 14 points and Patrick Tape scored 12. ------
